title: [MP3@320Kps]GRP Band - All star Big Band [TRK]
description:
The GRP Band was a group compiled in the late 1980's under the direction of Dave Grusin and Larry Rosen, principles of the GRP label. The band was a full band, and they mostly played well-known jazz pieces from the 1950's and 1960's written by famous musicians and composers. Many of these pieces were rearranged presenting a character of their own.
